commentTextItems.html: played to long on. India have won this match

commentPostTextItems.html: The presentation party consists of Dungarpur, Lele of BCCI and Ellman-Brown of ZCU
Talks about preparing better for the LG Cup in Kenya
As the crowd whistles and claps
Tendulkar "We are very happy about the performance"
Our batting was good, but more importantly the bowlers called the shots backed up by good fielding
Looks forward to the challenge tomorrow
Tendulkar picks up the winner cheque
Man of the match award also given to Tendulkar

commentTextItems.html: on the stumps, played back to the bowler
on the off, slow and straight, through to keeper as Whittall tries to late cut it and misses
